race.comment: PIERONIMO (8) is a consistent commodity who has hit the top-five at his past ten starts and strikes a very winnable contest here. Ready to peak now third-up from the spell and looks the one they all have to run down. MAKAMAE (15) got the job done here last time out and winning rider Sutherland sticks in the saddle. Again gets the benefit of his claim and rates a genuine top-three prospect against this line-up. WHATJEUDOIN' (17) is knocking on the door of another victory with three consecutive runner-up finishes. Can go one better from the inside marble. ARTSPACE (7) next in line with the 3kg off.
